      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "ELOHAI, n'tzor l'shoni meira us'fatai\nmidabeir mirmah, v'limkal'lai nafshi\ntidom, v'nafshi ke-afar lakol tih'yeh.\nP'tach libi b'Toratecha, uv'mitzvotecha\ntirdof nafshi. V'chol hachoshvim\nalai raah, m'heirah hafeir atzatam\nv'kalkeil machashavtam. Aseih I'maan\nsh'mecha, aseih I'maan y'minecha, aseih\nI'maan k'dushatecha, aseih I'maan\nToratecha. L'maan yeichaltzun y'didecha,\nhoshiah y'mincha vaaneini.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-17T16:50:45.976Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "xBAJpZLQa5VJbha9l2qO"
      },
      "image_url": "https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F2463c7a2-1d6a-49a7-93b0-b01f2f2919ca.jp2/412,389,1651,1848/max/0/default.jpg"
    },
    {
      "id": "9410ef58-1da6-4b86-8879-690b21e1a4ba",
      "target": {
        "source": "mishkan:page:2463c7a2-1d6a-49a7-93b0-b01f2f2919ca",
        "type": "SpecificResource",
        "selector": {
          "type": "FragmentSelector",
          "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
          "value": "xywh=pixel:412.73878835562545,2274.4295830055075,3510.306845003934,1069.7088906372937"
        }
      },
      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "MY GOD, guard my speech from evil and my lips from deception.\nBefore those who slander me, I will hold my tongue; I will practice humility.\nOpen my heart to Your Torah, that I may pursue Your mitzvot.\nAs for all who think evil of me, cancel their designs and frustrate their schemes.\nAct for Your own sake, for the sake of Your Power,\nfor the sake of Your Holiness, for the sake of Your Torah;\nso that Your loved ones may be rescued, save with Your power. And answer me.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-17T16:50:54.469Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "xBAJpZLQa5VJbha9l2qO"
      },
      "image_url": "https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F2463c7a2-1d6a-49a7-93b0-b01f2f2919ca.jp2/412,2274,3510,1069/max/0/default.jpg"
    },
    {
