        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "For those who count the Omer, every evening between Pesach and Shavuot, turn to page 570.\nReading of the Torah is on page 362. Aleinu and Kaddish are on pages 586–587.",
          "language": "en"
        }
