          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "Elohai, n'tzor l'shoni meira... My God, guard my speech from evil...\nbased on Psalm 34:14\nיֵחָלְצוּן\nph I'maan yeichaltzun... so that Your loved ones...\nPsalm 60:7\nYih'yu l'ratzon... May the words of my mouth... Psalm 19:15",
